metadata.name: Diesel - Expires 6/30/2022
metadata.description:
**Gems will expire on June 30th, 2022 at 11:59 PM ET. If you own a Gem, visit wolf.game/farmers to burn it to a Farmer before then.**

Strong in body, Diesel is here to put in the work.

This Gem can be redeemed during Farmer reveal to guarantee a Diesel Farmer.
